00:42:12,963 --> 00:42:15,239
What's with me today?

523
00:42:16,166 --> 00:42:18,168
It's because we're sad.

524
00:42:19,403 --> 00:42:24,409
Then cry instead of making jokes.

525
00:42:25,042 --> 00:42:27,283
I don't want to cry.

526
00:42:28,979 --> 00:42:31,357
Don't wanna make
someone cry even more.

527
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:40,166
I'm dying.
Just like my dad.

528
00:42:43,794 --> 00:42:45,501
Chul-kyu!

529
00:42:51,068 --> 00:42:55,676
<i>Mom left me a year after
Dad died.</i>

530
00:42:59,176 --> 00:43:02,089
<i>It probably wasn't
because she resented me.</i>

531
00:43:02,980 --> 00:43:05,517
<i>She was sick of everything
because of Dad.</i>

532
00:43:07,484 --> 00:43:12,229
<i>I understand.
I was sick of everything, too.</i>

533
00:43:13,324 --> 00:43:18,103
<i>But when she left me all alone...</i>

534
00:43:19,330 --> 00:43:21,537
<i>I was so lonely.</i>

535
00:43:25,235 --> 00:43:26,976
<i>People...</i>

536
00:43:28,172 --> 00:43:30,083
should never be alone.

537
00:43:59,336 --> 00:44:00,940
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

538
00:44:02,072 --> 00:44:04,143
<i>I want you to leave your fiancé.</i>

539
00:44:05,609 --> 00:44:07,977
<i>The girl that I love is
in love with him.</i>

540
00:44:07,778 --> 00:44:09,849
<i>- Medical records</i>

541
00:44:11,982 --> 00:44:13,586
<i>I beg you.</i>

542
00:44:21,625 --> 00:44:23,502
Under one condition.

543
00:44:26,397 --> 00:44:27,997
But...

544
00:44:27,998 --> 00:44:29,568
But?

545
00:44:36,440 --> 00:44:39,114
No, please!
Tell me.

546
00:44:50,487 --> 00:44:52,728
I want to take your pictures.

547
00:44:55,859 --> 00:45:01,366
Your medical records said
you don't have much time left.

548
00:45:02,599 --> 00:45:07,412
Now, that's an interesting model.

549
00:45:11,208 --> 00:45:13,484
I think it'll be fun.

550
00:45:13,677 --> 00:45:16,283
I don't think it'll be fun.

551
00:45:18,749 --> 00:45:20,695
Then the deal's off.

552
00:45:24,788 --> 00:45:26,825
Drink up, first!

553
00:45:27,124 --> 00:45:30,799
Give me a drink, too!

554
00:45:37,901 --> 00:45:40,780
- Hi! Hi!
- Hi! You're late!

555
00:45:45,342 --> 00:45:49,119
Hello.
I spoke to you on the phone.

556
00:45:49,780 --> 00:45:51,247
Oh, hi.

557
00:45:51,248 --> 00:45:52,522
I'm KANG Chul-kyu.

558
00:45:52,683 --> 00:45:53,957
CHA Joo-hwan.

559
00:45:54,051 --> 00:45:56,497
- Thanks again for that day.
- Anytime.

560
00:45:57,087 --> 00:45:58,464
You know him?

561
00:45:58,856 --> 00:46:00,233
The sterilizer?

562
00:46:03,293 --> 00:46:06,062
- Did you eat?
- No, I'll eat now.

563
00:46:06,063 --> 00:46:07,838
Why are you so late?

564
00:46:07,931 --> 00:46:10,377
- Still recording a show.
- What?

565
00:46:10,467 --> 00:46:11,934
You said you're done.

566
00:46:11,935 --> 00:46:14,472
Not yet.
I gotta go back.

567
00:46:17,174 --> 00:46:18,847
- Here.
- Thank you.

568
00:46:22,279 --> 00:46:25,089
The song's great.

569
00:46:26,083 --> 00:46:27,562
'If I can live again'?

570
00:46:27,651 --> 00:46:29,722
Of course, I wrote it.

571
00:46:31,155 --> 00:46:33,567
Sorry, I gotta run.

572
00:46:33,624 --> 00:46:37,629
- Come on.
- Don't go.

573
00:46:37,728 --> 00:46:39,139
I'll see you later.

574
00:46:39,596 --> 00:46:40,734
Bye.

575
00:46:41,365 --> 00:46:44,073
- See you next time, then.
- Sure.

576
00:46:49,373 --> 00:46:50,943
Be careful in the snow!